			</classificationInformation>
			<CASNumber>CID 7857</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Glycolonitrile is produced by reacting formaldehyde with hydrogen cyanide under acidic conditions. This reaction is catalysed by base. Glycolonitrile polymerizes under alkaline conditions above pH 7.0. As the product of polymerization is an amine with a basic character, the reaction is self-catalysed. Glycolonitrile is an organic compound with the structural formula of HOCH 2 CN, which is the simplest cyanohydrin that is derived by. Glycolonitrile is the result of reaction between formaldehyde and aqueous sodium cyanide in the presence of mineral acid.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">乙腈是由甲醛与氰化氢在酸性条件下反应生成的。该反应由碱催化。乙腈在 pH 值 7.0 以上的碱性条件下聚合。由于聚合反应的产物是具有碱性的胺，因此该反应是自催化的。乙腈是一种结构式为 HOCH 2 CN 的有机化合物，它是最简单的氰醇，可通过以下方法生成。乙腈是甲醛和氰化钠水溶液在矿物酸存在下反应的产物。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>HOCH2CN or C2H3NO</sumFormula>
